{"tid":1467350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家不如依加搞番個道歉運動啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:35.000Z","uid":175471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28f6b3bf17f4fdc8f9f85e1b204476c4230efc30","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"813~814<br />\n今晚既post 有好多都屌緊手足比仇恨支配左<br />\n如果係民意上做得唔好 好大機會會影響到場運動<br />\n<br />\n我知大家依加都好嬲好想打狗好想發洩<br />\n但係要諗下我地做緊既野係想成場運動成功定係想發洩打狗呢<br />\n建議聽日搞番到機場道歉行動show 比外國睇<br />\n我地依加香港時和理非仲係優質既<br />\n順便塞住班五毛把閪口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做唔係可以winwib 雙贏而且又可以順便佔機場<br />\nps 不分 不割 不篤"},{"pid":"9a9a6a4d32577cd1a0e7ca5d3204b9f8246bbc40","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"推一推先"},{"pid":"ce9438b6b106023dbbb04cccf0b2de23d915a5bc","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"33ab7030f9b51b3e9e6f538ea453872737ec7f58","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"3連"},{"pid":"e237fa482729c17e53be181d700070a050f958f6","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"4連"},{"pid":"622779fda9533f443f5d2e9cde1060ad0bfdc09f","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:52.000Z","msg":"5連"},{"pid":"87e316b006954f1da53f2f5c7ccc1f7f90d58ea5","tid":1467350,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"ad8c08586314b828b7d39856410ee53c10c7226f","tid":1467350,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"如得我講得唔岩既 講埋呢句就自己收皮<br />